Well, a maid is basically a woman, a female servant, so to say, a person that basically
嗯，女佣基本上是一个女人，一个女仆，可以说，一个为你

66
00:03:04,360 --> 00:03:05,360
serves you.
服务的人。

67
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,360
All right.
好的。

68
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,940
