所以她在家务活上工作。

72
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:22,640
But because there's a bad association, we don't like to think, oh, we have servants.
但因为有些不好的联想，我们不喜欢想，哦，我们有仆人。

73
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:24,240
We don't say maid anymore.
我们不再说“maid”了。

74
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:26,880
We have two other ways of saying this word.
我们有两种其他方式来说这个词。

75
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,880
That's right.
没错。

76
00:03:27,880 --> 00:03:31,720
So we could say that we want to hire a cleaning lady, right?
所以我们可以说想雇一个清洁女工，对吧？

77
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:34,080
Or we want to hire domestic help.
或者想雇家政帮手。

78
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,080
Okay.
好的。

79
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:37,160
