与房子相关的事情。

92
00:04:20,080 --> 00:04:25,960
So it's important to see that domestic means something that has to do with the house.
所以重要的是要明白“domestic”指的是与房子有关的事情。

93
00:04:25,960 --> 00:04:28,560
This is help man or woman in the house.
这是指家里的帮手，可以是男是女。

94
00:04:28,560 --> 00:04:29,560
Right.
对。

95
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,560
All right.
好的。

96
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:33,440
