00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,840
Fluency Builder.
流利度提升。

99
00:04:40,840 --> 00:04:41,840
All right.
好的。

100
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:47,920
So first on Fluency Builder, let's take a look at how we're going to pay the person
首先在“流利度提升”中，我们来看看如何支付这个人报酬，

101
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:50,440
