也不同于语言辅导老师的“going rate”。

133
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,920
Right.
对。

134
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:18,700
Or like an English tutor.
或者像英语辅导老师。

135
00:06:18,700 --> 00:06:25,000
So first of all, the going rate is how much these people, these cleaning ladies normally
首先，“going rate”是指这些人，这些清洁女工通常

136
00:06:25,000 --> 00:06:26,000
earn.
挣多少钱。

137
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:27,000
