它是一个平均值。

138
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,000
Right.
对。

139
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:33,040
So you would usually calculate it, say the approximate going rate is between maybe $8
所以你通常会估算一下，说大概的“going rate”可能在

140
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:34,880
to $10 per hour.
每小时八到十美元之间。

141
00:06:34,880 --> 00:06:36,520
So it's not like an exact amount.
所以它不是一个精确的金额。

142
00:06:36,520 --> 00:06:39,960
You would say the going rate is more or less a certain amount.
你会说“going rate”大致是某个数额。

143
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:41,280
It's not exact.
它不精确。

144
00:06:41,280 --> 00:06:44,400
So you might ask your friends, what do you pay your cleaning lady?
所以你可能会问朋友：你付给清洁女工多少钱？

145
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:47,640
And one friend says, oh, I pay $12 per hour.
一个朋友说，哦，我每小时付十二美元。

146
00:06:47,640 --> 00:06:51,440
