另一个朋友说，哦，我付大约每小时八美元。

147
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:56,440
So to me, it sounds like the going rate is about $10 per hour.
所以对我来说，听起来“going rate”大约是每小时十美元。

148
00:06:56,440 --> 00:06:57,440
Right.
对。

149
00:06:57,440 --> 00:06:58,440
Exactly.
完全正确。

150
00:06:58,440 --> 00:07:00,320
So we're not really sure what the going rate is.
所以我们不太确定“going rate”是多少。

151
00:07:00,320 --> 00:07:01,520
So our friend says, well, you know what?
所以我们的朋友说，嗯，你知道吗？

152
00:07:01,520 --> 00:07:05,440
I'm sure it's more than minimum wage.
我肯定它比“minimum wage”（最低工资）高。

153
