And each state will have a number that they say that is the least you can pay a person
每个州都会有一个数字，规定你每小时至少能付给一个人

156
00:07:19,320 --> 00:07:20,320
per hour.
多少钱。

157
00:07:20,320 --> 00:07:21,320
Right.
对。

158
00:07:21,320 --> 00:07:22,320
Right.
对。

