You can find us at EnglishPod.com.
你可以在EnglishPod.com找到我们。

277
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:36,740
We'll see you guys there.
我们那里见。

278
00:12:36,740 --> 00:12:37,740
Bye.
再见。

